          <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblJobText"><p><strong>Are you looking for an exciting position within the Gaming Industry?</strong><br />
- If you answered yes to this question; then you have come to the right place!<br />
<br />
GRIN is always looking for talented people to join our teams! GRIN can offer you an exciting and challenging career, spanning across the globe with our international offices in Barcelona, Jakarta, Gothenburg and Stockholm.<br />
<br />
GRIN has released many exciting titles, most recently the critically acclaimed title Bionic Commando Rearmed. Currently GRIN is in the process of developing Bionic Commando, Wanted and other great titles!<br />
<br />
Jump start your new career with GRIN!<br />
<br />
Please send you CV and work samples to job@grin.se<br />
<br />
If you have any questions, please call Gunnar Johansson. +46 8 20 30 95.</p></span></p>
